<title>USA: Sunbeam says in ad deal with Spanish network.</title>
<headline>Sunbeam says in ad deal with Spanish network.</headline>
<dateline>DELRAY BEACH, Fla. 1997-06-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Sunbeam Corp said Tuesday it entered into a partnership with United Family Communications for exclusive regional advertising on Casa Club TV, a network in Latin America.</p>
<p>Sunbeam said the move is part of a plan to increase international sales to $600 million by 1999.</p>
<p>United Family, a joint-venture between International Family Entertainment Inc and United International Holdings Inc, was formed to launch family-oriented networks in Latin America and Spain.</p>
<p>((New York Newsdesk 212 859 1610))</p>
